---
import OpenClawLayout from "../../layouts/OpenClawLayout.astro";
import "../../styles/quickstart-shared.css";
---

<OpenClawLayout
  title="OpenClaw Quickstart — Up and Running in 10 Minutes"
  description="Install OpenClaw, start the gateway, and get your personal AI agent running on Telegram or Discord in under 10 minutes."
  currentPage="quickstart"
>
  <div class="qs-wrapper">

    <header class="qs-hero">
      <span class="qs-hero__eyebrow">OpenClaw · Getting Started</span>
      <h1 class="qs-hero__title">
        Quick<span class="qs-hero__accent">Start</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="qs-hero__desc">Personal AI agent platform. Run your own AI on Telegram, Discord, Signal — or just your browser. Up and running in under 10 minutes.</p>
    </header>

    <div class="qs-journey">

      <div class="qs-step">
        <div class="qs-step__dot">01</div>
        <span class="qs-step__label">Prerequisites</span>
        <h2 class="qs-step__title">Node.js 18+ or Homebrew</h2>
        <p class="qs-step__desc">Check if you're ready — run these and confirm they return something.</p>
        <div class="qs-cmd-group">
          <div class="qs-cmd"><code><span class="qs-cmd__prompt">$</span>node --version</code></div>
          <div class="qs-cmd"><code><span class="qs-cmd__prompt">$</span>npm --version</code></div>
        </div>
        <p class="qs-cmd-note">Node 18 or higher required. If you're on macOS, Homebrew also works.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="qs-step">
        <div class="qs-step__dot">02</div>
        <span class="qs-step__label">Install</span>
        <h2 class="qs-step__title">Install OpenClaw globally</h2>
        <p class="qs-step__desc">Pick your preferred package manager. Both install the same thing.</p>
        <span class="qs-cmd-label">Option A — npm</span>
        <div class="qs-cmd"><code><span class="qs-cmd__prompt">$</span>npm install -g openclaw</code></div>
        <span class="qs-cmd-label">Option B — Homebrew (macOS)</span>
        <div class="qs-cmd"><code><span class="qs-cmd__prompt">$</span>brew install openclaw</code></div>
      </div>

      <div class="qs-step">
        <div class="qs-step__dot">03</div>
        <span class="qs-step__label">Onboard</span>
        <h2 class="qs-step__title">Run the setup wizard</h2>
        <p class="qs-step__desc">This creates your workspace, config files, and default agent. Only needed once.</p>
        <div class="qs-cmd"><code><span class="qs-cmd__prompt">$</span>openclaw onboard</code></div>
        <p class="qs-cmd-note">Follow the prompts. It will ask for a model API key — Anthropic, OpenAI, or OpenRouter all work.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="qs-step">
        <div class="qs-step__dot">04</div>
        <span class="qs-step__label">Start</span>
        <h2 class="qs-step__title">Start the gateway</h2>
        <p class="qs-step__desc">The gateway is the local process that routes messages between your channels and agents. It runs in the background.</p>
        <div class="qs-cmd"><code><span class="qs-cmd__prompt">$</span>openclaw gateway start</code></div>
      </div>

      <div class="qs-step qs-step--active">
        <div class="qs-step__dot">05</div>
        <span class="qs-step__label">Verify</span>
        <h2 class="qs-step__title">Open the dashboard — prove it works</h2>
        <p class="qs-step__desc">The dashboard runs in your browser. No messaging app needed yet. If you can chat here, the stack is working.</p>
        <div class="qs-cmd"><code><span class="qs-cmd__prompt">$</span>openclaw dashboard</code></div>
        <p class="qs-cmd-note">Opens at http://localhost:PORT — send a message to confirm your model is responding.</p>
      </div>

    </div>

    <div class="qs-milestone">
      <span class="qs-milestone__eyebrow">First Real Task</span>
      <h2 class="qs-milestone__title">Connect Telegram in 2 minutes</h2>
      <p class="qs-milestone__desc">Get your AI on your phone. Telegram is the fastest channel to set up — just a bot token and one command.</p>
      <div class="qs-milestone__steps">
        <div class="qs-milestone__step">
          <div class="qs-milestone__step-num">1</div>
          <div class="qs-milestone__step-body">Open Telegram, message <code>@BotFather</code>, send <code>/newbot</code>, follow the steps, copy the token.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="qs-milestone__step">
          <div class="qs-milestone__step-num">2</div>
          <div class="qs-milestone__step-body">Run the command below with your token.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="qs-milestone__cmd"><code><span class="qs-cmd__prompt">$</span>openclaw channels add --channel telegram --token YOUR_BOT_TOKEN</code></div>
      <div class="qs-milestone__steps">
        <div class="qs-milestone__step">
          <div class="qs-milestone__step-num">3</div>
          <div class="qs-milestone__step-body">Open the dashboard QR code and scan it from your phone to approve the pairing. Done — your AI is now in your Telegram DMs.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="qs-next">
      <p class="qs-next__title">What next?</p>
      <div class="qs-next__grid">
        <a href="/openclaw/tips/" class="qs-next__card">
          <span class="qs-next__card-arrow">⚡</span>
          <div class="qs-next__card-title">Tips & Tricks</div>
          <p class="qs-next__card-desc">Power user moves, hidden features, and mistakes to avoid.</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/openclaw/cheatsheet/" class="qs-next__card">
          <span class="qs-next__card-arrow">📋</span>
          <div class="qs-next__card-title">Cheatsheet</div>
          <p class="qs-next__card-desc">Every command, flag, and workflow at a glance.</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/openclaw/changelog/" class="qs-next__card">
          <span class="qs-next__card-arrow">🔔</span>
          <div class="qs-next__card-title">Changelog</div>
          <p class="qs-next__card-desc">Stay current with every release.</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/openclaw/configs/" class="qs-next__card">
          <span class="qs-next__card-arrow">⚙️</span>
          <div class="qs-next__card-title">Configs</div>
          <p class="qs-next__card-desc">Full configuration reference.</p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>

  <script is:inline>
    document.querySelectorAll('.qs-cmd').forEach(function(block) {
      var btn = document.createElement('button');
      btn.className = 'qs-cmd__copy';
      btn.textContent = 'copy';
      btn.addEventListener('click', function() {
        var code = block.querySelector('code');
        if (!code) return;
        var text = code.textContent.replace(/^\$\s*/, '').replace(/^\$/, '').trim();
        navigator.clipboard.writeText(text).then(function() {
          btn.textContent = 'copied!';
          setTimeout(function() { btn.textContent = 'copy'; }, 1500);
        });
      });
      block.style.paddingRight = '5rem';
      block.appendChild(btn);
    });
  </script>
</OpenClawLayout>
